reviewText: It was too old I didn't like it
Received in a timely manner as advertised.
Love it. Grew up watching these great comics.

There's an empty disc-holder for an EIGHTH disc in the 7-disc
DEAN MARTIN CELEBRITY ROASTS Collection... cannot think
of a better place to put MY copy!

All too short but interesting and funn look at and into the Friars Club.
Sorry that there wasn.t more from the actual "Roasts".
